    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Try checking your CompIds and sequence numbers. These are the top two reasons we see login failures. Especially when setting up a new session, check you have the SenderCompId and TargetCompId the right way around, it's surprisingly easy to mix up! </p>\n"
